pic_server
==========

Web site that stores and organizes pictures.

This will import pictures from a directory and 
slurp them into a file system and use a database
to keep track of them.  

Features : 
 - rotate pictures
 - tag pictures 
 - add comments to pictures
 - automatically generates thumbnails
 - group pictures by event
 - gets EXIF data 

Installation : 
 - Requires Java / JSP and imagemagic to be installed
 - to create the database tables run web/scripts/create_tables.txt


